        "created_at": "2019-08-04T21:51:16.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/wine.asp?iWine=2578475\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>2014 Domaine Martelet de Cherisey Puligny-Montrachet 1er Cru Hameau de Blagny</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Beaune, Puligny-Montrachet 1er Cru (8/4/2019)</em><br>\nExcellent. Nervous acidity frames beautiful perfectly ripe  lemon yellow fruit. Great finish and this will only get much better.  Mineral.   Developing more complexity with time will make this truly outstanding.   Out of magnum.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
